The "Mojikyo Study Society" has concluded the Agreement on Entrustment of Distribution with AI-Net Corporation which is the copyright holder with respect to the right to distribute the "Konjaku-Mojikyo Fonts" and the "Software to Utilize the Konjaku- Mojikyo Fonts" that are furnished by the "Mojikyo Font Center." Under the Agreement mentioned above, the "Mojikyo Study Society" shall have an authority to distribute the "Konjaku-Mojikyo Fonts" and the "Software to Utilize the Konjaku-Mojikyo Fonts" which include data and tools to be renewed. All administration businesses shall be handled by the "Mojikyo Font Center" operated by the Mojikyo Study Society. Main businesses are as follows:
1. 	 Collection of characters that have not as yet been gathered and recorded in the "Konjaku-Mojikyo";
2. 	Distribution of the Konjaku-Mojikyo fonts, including those characters which have already been contained in and newly added to the "Konjaku-Mojikyo";
3. 	Distribution of the software to utilize the Konjaku-Mojikyo fonts; and
4. 	Distribution of the "Image Mark Specifying the Use of the Konjaku-Mojikyo Fonts."
